linhello (0.4.2-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Packaging: floor the Fedora onnxruntime weak dependency at >= 1.24 to enforce
    the ort 2.0.0-rc.12 / ONNX Runtime 1.24.x ABI pairing. Debian vendors ONNX
    Runtime out-of-band (linhello fetch-onnx), so there is no apt dependency to
    floor here; the version is synced with the workspace. No code change.

